    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142540/extras/5d726515022370607811fcb9a7f69218.avif?t=1756904384\" width=600 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142540/extras/669dacea3fa4581252d7099ceaa4354c.webp?t=1756904384\" width=600 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以<i>星球工匠</i>的身份，踏上<strong>全新星球</strong><strong>“汉布尔星”</strong>的重启征程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论孤身一人，还是与好友同行，探索这片未知之地，揭开它背后的故事和隐藏的秘密，再度肩负起改造整颗星球的使命！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142540/extras/e027c79fdd6145f84c71929c1e8131f2.webp?t=1756904384\" width=600 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>只需购买一份 DLC</strong>，即可与好友联机共游，共享全新内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142540/extras/3b9631e1dd9fe075cda0fd4c26c65bf5.webp?t=1756904384\" width=600 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一场全新的冒险——登陆<strong>面积为主星一半的汉布尔星<strong>，探索众多前所未见的生物群落。[/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142540/extras/1289e93295754f7a1b60e850058228a2.webp?t=1756904384\" width=600 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这颗星球为何无人居住？踏上这片新世界，揭开围绕太空殖民与巨型财团的全新剧情线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142540/extras/4e22b0cddec4cc6a80c2da2f54ddfab8.webp?t=1756904384\" width=600 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安营扎寨，打造你梦想中的探索基地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要游玩“汉布尔”DLC，有两种方式：创建新存档，并选择星球“<i>汉布尔星</i>”；或在完成主星的改造后，通过游戏内的星际系统前往汉布尔星。</p></strong></strong></p>",
